            <title>[KAFKA-16203] AutoCommit of empty offsets blocks following requests due to inflight flag</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-16203</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
